{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Spring/211227-view-build/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"@gintooooonic","author":"gintooooonic","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6c7cf25b-e177-5578-8d51-8c115537a229","excerpt":"Welcome 페이지 추가하기  경로에\n 파일을 생성하고 다음 내용을 입력한다. 스프링 부트는  정적 페이지를 먼저 찾고,\n없으면  템플릿을 찾아 Welcome 페이지로 사용한다고\n공식 문서에서 언급하고 있다. localhost:8080으로\n접속하면 Welcome 페이지를 확인할 수 있다.  Thymeleaf 템플릿 엔진 정적 페이지가 아니라\nThymeleaf…","html":"<h2 id=\"welcome-페이지-추가하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#welcome-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"welcome 페이지 추가하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Welcome 페이지 추가하기</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">src/main/resources/static</code> 경로에\n<code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code> 파일을 생성하고 다음 내용을 입력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Welcome<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Welcome<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Welcome! Move to <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/hello<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>/hello<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>스프링 부트는 <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code> 정적 페이지를 먼저 찾고,\n없으면 <code class=\"language-text\">index</code> 템플릿을 찾아 Welcome 페이지로 사용한다고\n<a href=\"https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/2.3.1.RELEASE/reference/html/spring-boot-features.html#boot-features-spring-mvc-welcome-page\">공식 문서</a>에서 언급하고 있다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080\">localhost:8080</a>으로\n접속하면 Welcome 페이지를 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1182px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"welcome_page\"\n        title=\"welcome_page\"\n        src=\"/static/e5b6e10a69125ef5b8af096909286944/7161f/welcome_page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5b6e10a69125ef5b8af096909286944/5a46d/welcome_page.png 300w,\n/static/e5b6e10a69125ef5b8af096909286944/0a47e/welcome_page.png 600w,\n/static/e5b6e10a69125ef5b8af096909286944/7161f/welcome_page.png 1182w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1182px) 100vw, 1182px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"thymeleaf-템플릿-엔진\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#thymeleaf-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EC%97%94%EC%A7%84\" aria-label=\"thymeleaf 템플릿 엔진 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thymeleaf 템플릿 엔진</h2>\n<p>정적 페이지가 아니라\nThymeleaf 템플릿 엔진을 사용해 페이지를 제공할 수도 있다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">/hello</code> 경로로 접근시 제공할 페이지를 작성하려고 한다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">com.hello.startspring.controller</code> 패키지를 생성하고,\n그 안에 <code class=\"language-text\">HelloController</code> 클래스를 추가한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 644px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hello_controller\"\n        title=\"hello_controller\"\n        src=\"/static/dd81c9a9fdc6f56d75f841fb79fed2e5/78274/hello_controller.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd81c9a9fdc6f56d75f841fb79fed2e5/5a46d/hello_controller.png 300w,\n/static/dd81c9a9fdc6f56d75f841fb79fed2e5/0a47e/hello_controller.png 600w,\n/static/dd81c9a9fdc6f56d75f841fb79fed2e5/78274/hello_controller.png 644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">HelloController</code> 클래스에 다음과 같은 코드를 작성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">package</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">com<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hello<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startspring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>controller</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>springframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stereotype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Controller</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>springframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ui<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>springframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>web<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bind<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>annotation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">GetMapping</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Controller</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HelloController</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@GetMapping</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Model</span> model<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"user\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Spring\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">HelloController</code> 클래스 위에 <code class=\"language-text\">@Controller</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">@GetMapping(\"hello\")</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">/hello</code>라는 경로에 대해\n해당 메서드(hello)를 매핑한다는 의미이다.\nGet은 HTTP 메서드의 그 Get 맞다.</li>\n<li>hello() 메서드는 Model을 인자로 받아 <code class=\"language-text\">user</code>라는 이름에\n<code class=\"language-text\">Spring</code>이라는 속성을 추가하고, 문자열 <code class=\"language-text\">\"hello\"</code>를 반환한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>hello() 메서드가 문자열 <code class=\"language-text\">\"hello\"</code>를 반환함으로써\n<code class=\"language-text\">hello</code>라는 이름을 가진 템플릿을 사용하게 된다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">src/main/resources/templates</code> 경로에\n<code class=\"language-text\">hello.html</code> 파일을 생성하고 다음 내용을 입력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>th</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.thymeleaf.org<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Hello<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Hello<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>text</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>Hello, <span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span> + ${user}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Hello, Guest.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/hello\">localhost:8080/hello</a>\n에 접속해보니 이런 페이지를 출력한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1182px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hello_page\"\n        title=\"hello_page\"\n        src=\"/static/99201bc35d18aa743a80325b7c4c36de/7161f/hello_page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/99201bc35d18aa743a80325b7c4c36de/5a46d/hello_page.png 300w,\n/static/99201bc35d18aa743a80325b7c4c36de/0a47e/hello_page.png 600w,\n/static/99201bc35d18aa743a80325b7c4c36de/7161f/hello_page.png 1182w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1182px) 100vw, 1182px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>컨트롤러에서 <code class=\"language-text\">addAttribute()</code>를 통해 추가했던 이름-값 속성이\n템플릿 엔진에 의해 적용되었음을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-빌드-및-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EB%B9%8C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 빌드 및 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 빌드 및 실행</h2>\n<p>프로젝트 최상위 경로에서 터미널을 실행해 다음 명령어를 입력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 빌드</span>\n./gradlew build\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 클린 빌드</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># ./gradle clean build</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 빌드된 경로로 이동</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> build/libs\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 실행</span>\njava -jar start-spring-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%9E%85%EB%AC%B8-%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81%EB%B6%80%ED%8A%B8\">김영한, 스프링 입문 - 코드로 배우는 스프링 부트, 웹 MVC, DB 접근 기술</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/2.3.1.RELEASE/reference/html/spring-boot-features.html\">Spring Boot Features - Spring</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211227-view-build/#welcome-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Welcome 페이지 추가하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211227-view-build/#thymeleaf-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EC%97%94%EC%A7%84\">Thymeleaf 템플릿 엔진</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211227-view-build/#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EB%B9%8C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">프로젝트 빌드 및 실행</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/211227-view-build/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"뷰 작성 및 프로젝트 빌드해보기","date":"December 27, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Spring/211227-view-build/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Java/211227-parse-format/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"파싱과 포맷팅"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Java/211230-collection-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"컬렉션 프레임워크 하나, List"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}